1664090ed508dd893d4cdaf3fe113b9bb239b","tid":1285001,"uid":61830,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0cdf4125b3c2bb91a24578f944d77dc7ca5a8fcd","tid":1285001,"uid":70007,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-04T13:05:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-04T13:46:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-04T17:11:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-04T17:14:57.000Z","msg":"有錢去玩下"},{"pid":"cbfd2ace5e4f71a7455443424b727b89ea680c21","tid":1285001,"uid":122513,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"30bd7ec7bbaaf8cb4774eb50ddba2c3fd241b07c","tid":1285001,"uid":70007,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-04T11:44:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-05T11:08:23.000Z","msg":"你好，這是《自殺．自療．互助舍》。看來你已累積了不少負面情緒，是嗎？人就好像氣球一樣，若積存的鬱結和壓力太多，便會有爆發的一天。何不暫時停一停，<a href=\"http://到我們的網站www.help4suicide.com.hk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2F%E5%88%B0%E6%88%91%E5%80%91%E7%9A%84%E7%B6%B2%E7%AB%99www.help4suicide.com.hk&d=mquyjxz0VyBhytkWBmIwRa3e3GGuF%2FCnRpDBLK0zENU%3D&h=deb1c60b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">到我們的網站www.help4suicide.com.hk</a>。 那裡有一些勵志故事和有趣短片，你可以隨心看看。你也可以進入網站內的『Chat窿』（星期一至五：上午六時至凌晨一時；星期六、日及公眾假期：下午８時至凌晨１時），讓我們的義工為你加油打氣！<br />\n <br />\n我們願意聆聽你的心聲，伴你一起走過這段艱難的時候！只因『晴天雨天要樂天，難關難過總會過』！<br />\n<br />\n《自殺．自療．互助舍》"},{"pid":"0cf636d0b387b7a1fe9c712413b33c7b2bd69e6e","tid":1285001,"uid":219340,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-05T13:12:25.000Z","msg":"非常明白，處境一樣。<br />\n個人冇力到收左工就要訓低，起唔到身咁滯"}]}